            "body": "Seems to have been missed since \"Remove deprecated functions marked for removal (`vim.deprecate(…, '0.12')`)\" in #33066 was never completed.\r\n\r\nOther stuff like updating the [sponsors page](https://github.com/sponsors/neovim) also isn't done:\r\n\r\n> Our next focus is towards Nvim 0.12 in 2025.\r\n\r\n:)",
