            "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
            "body": "Thanks, I was not sure why these functions were still being kept... I'm just planning to move forward with the plan to use `vim.pos`/`vim.range` to reduce the number of functions in `vim.lsp.util`.\r\n\r\nEdit: Since this appeared to be an oversight, I expanded the scope of the removal to include deprecated functions outside of the LSP as well.",
